  "strategy": [
    "Prioritize marker_seen: immediately switch to marker_track state to approach marker.",
    "On marker_lost during tracking, switch to scan_full to reacquire marker.",
    "On marker_close, always transition to goal_stop (terminal) state where only stop is allowed.",
    "Handle all obstacle events in every state to ensure safety; never allow move_forward from obs_front.",
    "After obstacle recovery, always pass through scan_full before resuming exploration.",
    "In clear, allow both move_forward and full_rotate to balance exploration and marker search.",
    "In obs_left, prefer rotate_commit_cw; in obs_right, prefer rotate_commit_ccw to avoid oscillations.",
    "Commit states (forward_commit, rotate_commit_*) are one-shot: after action, return to clear or appropriate state.",
    "Alternate forward_commit and scan_full in search to avoid long straight runs without scanning.",
    "All uncontrollable events are handled deterministically and totally in every state."
  ]
